---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Book a Call | How to Fund Travel"
  description="Schedule a personalized consultation to discuss your family travel funding goals and get expert guidance on achieving location independence."
  canonical="https://howtofund.travel/book-a-call"
  type="website"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Hero
    badgeIcon="üí¨"
    badgeText="Personalized Consultation"
    title="Let's Chat About Your "
    highlightText="Travel Dreams"
    subtitle="Ready to turn your family travel dreams into reality? Book a personalized consultation to discuss your goals, challenges, and the best path forward for your unique situation."
    showStats={true}
    customStats={[
      { icon: "üéØ", text: "Personalized<br>Strategy" },
      { icon: "‚è∞", text: "15-Minute<br>Session" },
      { icon: "üí°", text: "Actionable<br>Insights" }
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Booking Section -->
  <section class="booking-section" aria-labelledby="booking-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro">
        <h2 id="booking-heading">Schedule Your Free Call</h2>
        <p>Choose a time that works for you and let's discuss your family travel funding goals.</p>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="booking-content">
        <div class="booking-info">
          <h3>What to Expect</h3>
          <ul class="expectations-list">
            <li><strong>Personal Assessment:</strong> We'll discuss your current situation and travel goals</li>
            <li><strong>Strategy Discussion:</strong> Explore the best funding methods for your family</li>
            <li><strong>Next Steps:</strong> Get a clear action plan tailored to your needs</li>
            <li><strong>Q&A:</strong> Ask any questions about location independence and travel funding</li>
          </ul>
          
          <div class="booking-note">
            <h4>Before Our Call</h4>
            <p>Take a moment to think about:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Your family's travel timeline and goals</li>
              <li>Current income sources and skills</li>
              <li>Biggest challenges or concerns</li>
              <li>What success looks like for your family</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="booking-calendar">
          <h3>Select Your Preferred Time</h3>
          <div class="tidycal-embed" data-path="gypsy/15-minute-meeting"></div>
          <script src="https://asset-tidycal.b-cdn.net/js/embed.js" async></script>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro">
        <h2 id="faq-heading">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-content">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is this consultation really free?</h3>
          <p>Yes! This consultation is completely free. I believe in providing value upfront and helping families understand their options before making any commitments.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What if I'm not ready to start traveling yet?</h3>
          <p>That's perfectly fine! Many families start planning years in advance. We can discuss your timeline and create a roadmap for achieving your goals, whether you want to start next month or in a few years.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do I need to prepare anything?</h3>
          <p>No formal preparation required, but it helps to have a general idea of your travel goals and current situation. The more specific you can be about your dreams, the more targeted advice I can provide.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What if I need more help after our call?</h3>
          <p>During our consultation, I'll let you know about additional resources, courses, or coaching options that might be helpful for your specific situation. There's no pressure to purchase anything.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Lemon Tuesday font is now loaded from local file via main.css */

  /* Hero Section */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: url('/images/optimized/ocean-shores-transparency.webp') no-repeat center center;
    background-size: cover;
    min-height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--dark);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 25px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .hero .highlight {
    font-family: 'Lemon Tuesday', 'Shadows Into Light', cursive;
    color: #2A9D8F;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-text {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    opacity: 0.9;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  /* Booking Section */
  .booking-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }

  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-intro h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2A9D8F;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-intro p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: #F4A261;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .booking-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .booking-info h3 {
    color: #2A9D8F;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .expectations-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .expectations-list li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .expectations-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .expectations-list strong {
    color: #2A9D8F;
  }

  .booking-note {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .booking-note h4 {
    color: #2A9D8F;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .booking-note p {
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .booking-note ul {
    color: #666;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .booking-note li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .booking-calendar {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .booking-calendar h3 {
    color: #2A9D8F;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* FAQ Section */
  .faq-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .faq-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq-item {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border-left: 4px solid #2A9D8F;
  }

  .faq-item h3 {
    color: #2A9D8F;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-stats {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .booking-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .section-intro h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
